Inspiration is a feature in Dungeons & Dragons where you are awarded one inspiring moment by the Dungeon master carrying forth into your memory,
usually given for unusually good roleplaying or cleverness and can later spend that moment-point on rerolling the most common dice in the game,
the D20.

Here are the best links I could find for pulling this whole thing off.



